thread.title_full: Wall Art Prints reviewed by Ruth

author: Ruth
title: Ruth
text: I needed to change the size I ordered because I had misjudged the measurements. The lady I dealt with was most helpful and solved the problem instantly. The print, when it arrived, was exactly what I wanted. I love it and will certainly use this Wall Art Prints again. Definitely worth five stars.
